NUMBER 646
NAME High in the Shartans
AERIAL
DROPLOC 712
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
From here, you can see dozens of miles in almost any direction. The lone
exception is the northwest. There, you see a looming peak, one of the most
prominent in the area. On a plateau, you see a pillar of gleaming light.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NW 647
EXIT BELOW 4
