NUMBER 2133
NAME Sky Over Grymwood
AERIAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are flying over the dense green Grymwood Forest. The expanse of the great green lake of life spreads out below you like a blanket over the soil of Andor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 2125
EXIT S 2141
EXIT E 2134
EXIT W 2132
EXIT NE 2126
EXIT SW 2140
EXIT NW 2124
EXIT SE 2142
EXIT BELOW 160
IFPREVERB CONCENTRATE -1
 IFCARRY 1861 -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You circle the skies eyeing the forest below you as you spot the terrace...
   ECHO OTHERS %N flies in a series of wide arcing circles.
   EQUAL FLAG3 1
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER The vista of the woods below makes you long for the shelter of your shroud.
   ECHO OTHERS %n looks down and shivers.
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DESCEND -1
 IFVAR FLAG3 = 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You orient yourself on the hidden terrace in the trees below and descend...
  ECHO OTHERS %n sweeps in an intricate circle and descends into the trees below.
  MOVE 2442
  AFFECT 2442
  ECHO OTHERS %n sweeps in from the sky above.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
